WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.670 --> 00:00:05.410
Zhang Peizan: Yes, I came back from walking the horses that day.

2
00:00:05.410 --> 00:00:08.760
Zhang Peizan: Just when I walked to the garden, I heard the young lady and her fiancé talking.

3
00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:09.910
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

4
00:00:09.910 --> 00:01:14.490
Zhang Peizan: She asked him to come to the garden in the middle of the night to get gold.

5
00:01:14.490 --> 00:01:16.890
Zhang Peizan: Feelings of greed stirred in my heart at that moment.

6
00:01:16.890 --> 00:01:21.840
Chorus (singing): ♪ He said that he stole a hairpin because he was greedy for gold ♪

7
00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:28.980
Chorus (singing): ♪ and quietly waited outside the garden for Xuechun. ♪

8
00:01:28.980 --> 00:01:38.220
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

9
00:01:38.220 --> 00:01:46.900
Chorus (singing): ♪ He clapped his hands three times so that the gate would open, and he could exchange the hairpin for money without any hindrance. ♪

10
00:01:46.900 --> 00:01:51.520
[Zhang Peizan clears throat]

11
00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:52.790
Xuechun: Mr. Lin,

12
00:01:52.790 --> 00:01:55.770
Xuechun: you must not let my lady’s kindness go to waste.

13
00:01:55.770 --> 00:02:01.300
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

14
00:02:01.300 --> 00:02:02.820
Xuechun: It's getting late,

15
00:02:02.820 --> 00:02:05.000
Xuechun: please go back.

16
00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:08.570
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

17
00:02:08.570 --> 00:02:11.750
Chorus (singing): ♪ Flustered, legs trembling, ♪

18
00:02:11.750 --> 00:02:14.300
Chorus (singing): ♪ he fell to the ground and ruined his plan. ♪

19
00:02:14.300 --> 00:02:15.530
Xuechun: Mr. Lin?

20
00:02:15.530 --> 00:02:18.000
Chorus: ♪ Xuechun recognized who it was and shouted loudly. ♪

21
00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:19.460
Xuechun: Ah, it’s you!

22
00:02:19.460 --> 00:02:20.730
Zhang Peizan: Don't shout.

23
00:02:20.730 --> 00:02:22.750
Zhang Peizan: If you shout, I will kill you.

24
00:02:22.750 --> 00:02:27.020
Chorus (singing): ♪ One mistake of his caused her soul to travel to the underworld. ♪

25
00:02:27.020 --> 00:02:28.180
Xuechun: Help!

26
00:02:28.180 --> 00:02:29.500
Xuechun: Help!

27
00:02:29.500 --> 00:02:31.500
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

28
00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:33.720
Zhang Peizan: I just managed to hide the knife and the gold.

29
00:02:33.720 --> 00:02:35.880
Zhang Peizan: I saw Lin coming over, so he became my scapegoat!